{"id":320745,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/11/美国之音-中国广西炮竹厂爆炸造成伤亡/","date":"2013-11-02T12:33:21Z","modified":"2013-11-02T19:20:03Z","title":"美国之音 | 中国广西炮竹厂爆炸造成伤亡","content":"<div>中国国家媒体和地方官员说，中国南部广西一座炮竹厂爆炸，造成至少11人死亡，17人受伤。</div>\n<p>官方的新华社说，多数死伤者都是女工。</p>\n<p>爆炸星期五发生在广西梧州岑溪市三堡镇车河村炮竹厂。整座工厂被炸为废墟。附近建筑也感到晃动，并有玻璃破碎。官媒报道说，工厂负责人已被警方控制，当局下令抢救受伤人员并尽快查明事故原因并立即开始安全生产大检查。</p>\n<p>工作场所的安全性在中国是一大问题。</p>\n<div><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://fullrss.net/v/b5751a1dab57f57671c5d503ab58280b/http/www.voachinese.com/content/china-firework-blast-20131102/1782034.html\" /></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://fullrss.net/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">fullrss.net</a></div>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/embeddedform?hl=zh-CN&amp;formkey=dGRpN3FrVThuMFFsZHBZcmNGLW94dEE6MQ\" height=\"326\" width=\"510\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\"></iframe></p>\n<form action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&amp;id=b4fd4ae247\" method=\"POST\"><a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代 </a></p>\n<p><input id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" style=\"display: block;\" type=\"email\" name=\"EMAIL\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required=\"\" size=\"25\" value=\"\" /><br />\n<input id=\"in_post_subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" type=\"submit\" name=\"subscribe\" value=\"点击订阅\" /></p>\n</form>\n","author":998,"categories":[18270,18269,10466,8779],"tags":[8889,24092,12012]}